          <mj-text>
            <h3>More Summer Music Happenings</h3>
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>

        <mj-column width="35%">
          <mj-image src="http://objects-us-west-1.dream.io/email-images/june-17/rockygrass-2017.jpg" />
        </mj-column>

        <mj-column width="65%">
          <mj-text>
            <span class="date">RockyGrass!</span>
            <p>This <span class="date">July 28-30th</span> marks our 10th year broadcasting live from <a href="http://www.bluegrass.com/rockygrass/">RockyGrass</a>, featuring Del McCoury, Sam Bush Bluegrass Band, Earls of Leicester, Infamous Stringdusters and many more.</p>
            <p>In addition to our regular complete live stream of the festival via <a href="http://kgnu.org">KGNU.org</a> and <a href="http://www.afterfm.com/index.cfm/fuseaction/rocky.grass">AfterFM.com </a>, we’ll be broadcasting more of the music from the festival over our airwaves than ever before, We hope you’ll join us at the festival or through our broadcast for this exciting Colorado music event, now in its 45th year.
            </p>
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>

        <mj-column width="35%">
          <mj-image src="http://objects-us-west-1.dream.io/email-images/june-17/arise-2017.jpg" />
        </mj-column>

        <mj-column width="65%">
          <mj-text>
            <span class="date">Arise!</span>
            <p>The following weekend, <span class="date">August 4-6</span>, KGNU will also provide an AfterFM live stream of the <a href="http://arisefestival.com/">Arise Music Festival</a>. Check in with our <a href="http://www.afterfm.com/index.cfm/fuseaction/content.detail/contentID/121/pageTitle/Arise%20Music%20Festival%202017">streaming page</a> for updates on our streaming schedule as the festival approaches.</p>
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>

        <mj-column width="100%">
          <mj-text>
            These are only a few of the music-related events KGNU will be involved in this summer, so check out our <a href="http://www.afterfm.com/index.cfm/fuseaction/content.kgnuPresentsListings/showing/1">complete list</a> of KGNU concerts and outreach events in the coming months.
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
